// Journal Entries (1.000.000++)
@1000002 = ~Montaron's Equipment

Montaron lost all of his equipment when he died to the Harpers.
Now we need to go to his and Xzar's old base in the Docks to get one of his tools he stashed there.~

//Evil
@1000003 = ~Montaron's Equipment

Upon entering Xzar's old base we walked into a Zhentarim Thief looting the place.
We killed the Thief and retrieved Montaron's Dagger.~

// Good
@1000004 = ~Montaron's Equipment

Upon entering Xzar's old base we walked into a Zhentarim Thief looting the place.
We let the Thief go upon taking Montaron's Dagger from him.~